{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/til/technical-writing/one/03-clear-sentence/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"bestalign's dev blog","categories":[{"displayText":"홈","priority":0,"name":"home","url":"/"},{"displayText":"TIL","priority":1,"name":"til","url":"/til"},{"displayText":"개발","priority":2,"name":"dev","url":"/dev"},{"displayText":"독서","priority":3,"name":"reading","url":"/reading"},{"displayText":"번역","priority":4,"name":"translation","url":"/translation"},{"displayText":"일기","priority":5,"name":"everydaylife","url":"/everydaylife"}]}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"d8817522-bc06-5dba-b103-d748845b075d","excerpt":"적절한 동사를 사용하라 정확하고 명확한 동사를 사용하라. 다음과 같은 몇 개의 동사만 돌려쓰면 지루하다. be 동사 occur happen Examples When a variable declaration doesn’t have a datatype, a compiler errors…","html":"<h4 id=\"적절한-동사를-사용하라\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%81%EC%A0%88%ED%95%9C-%EB%8F%99%EC%82%AC%EB%A5%BC-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EB%9D%BC\" aria-label=\"적절한 동사를 사용하라 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>적절한 동사를 사용하라</h4>\n<p>정확하고 명확한 동사를 사용하라. 다음과 같은 몇 개의 동사만 돌려쓰면 지루하다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>be 동사</li>\n<li>occur</li>\n<li>happen</li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"examples\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#examples\" aria-label=\"examples permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Examples</h5>\n<p>When a variable declaration doesn’t have a datatype, a compiler errors happens. <br/>\n=> When a variable declaration doesn’t specify a datatype, the compiler generates an error message.</p>\n<p>Compiler errors occur when you leave off a semicolon at the end of a statement. <br/>\n=> A missing semicolon at the end of a statement triggers compiler errors.</p>\n<h4 id=\"there-isthere-are-의-사용을-줄여라\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#there-isthere-are-%EC%9D%98-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%EC%9D%84-%EC%A4%84%EC%97%AC%EB%9D%BC\" aria-label=\"there isthere are 의 사용을 줄여라 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>There is/There are 의 사용을 줄여라</h4>\n<p>There is/There are는 지루하다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>문장 내에 진짜 주어와 동사가 있는 경우가 있다. 그럴 경우 There is/There are을 없애고 완전한 문장으로 만들어라.</li>\n<li>문장 내에 진짜 동사가 없는 경우도 있다. 적당한 동사를 만들어서 완전한 문장으로 바꾸어라.</li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"examples-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#examples-1\" aria-label=\"examples 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Examples</h5>\n<p>There is a variable called <code class=\"language-text\">met_trick</code> that stores the current accuracy. <br/>\n=> A varaible called <code class=\"language-text\">met_trick</code> stores the current accuracy.</p>\n<p>There is no guarantee that the updates will be received in sequential order. <br/>\n=> Clients might not receive the updates in sequential order.</p>\n<h4 id=\"형용사와-부사는-조심해서-사용하라\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%98%95%EC%9A%A9%EC%82%AC%EC%99%80-%EB%B6%80%EC%82%AC%EB%8A%94-%EC%A1%B0%EC%8B%AC%ED%95%B4%EC%84%9C-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EB%9D%BC\" aria-label=\"형용사와 부사는 조심해서 사용하라 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>형용사와 부사는 조심해서 사용하라</h4>\n<p>형용사와 부사는 테크니컬 문서에서 사용하기에 충분히 정확하게 정의되어 있지 않다. 읽는 사람의 관심을 끌어낼 수 있을지는 몰라도 그 뿐이다. 형용사와 부사 대신 객관적인 숫자를 이용하라.</p>\n<h5 id=\"example\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#example\" aria-label=\"example permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Example</h5>\n<p>Setting this flag makes the application run screamingly fast. <br/>\n=> Setting this flag makes the application run 3 times faster.</p>\n<h4 id=\"reference\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reference\" aria-label=\"reference permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Reference</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://developers.google.com/tech-writing/one/clear-sentences\">Google Dev Technical Writing 1 - clear sentence</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"테크니컬 라이팅 - Clear Sentence","category":"til","date":"June 29, 2021","updated":null,"description":null,"tags":["technical writing"]}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/til/technical-writing/one/02-active-voice/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"테크니컬 라이팅 - Active Voice"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/til/technical-writing/one/04-short-sentence-1/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"테크니컬 라이팅 - Short Sentence 1"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"d8817522-bc06-5dba-b103-d748845b075d","previousPostId":"0cb8b622-33f3-5122-ae7b-a29065908e78","nextPostId":"6a2f5eb9-f2c6-5aba-a74b-66a816c02e29"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383"]}